                            "property": {
                                "card": "{card}",
                                "mergeField": "%3Cdiv%3E%3Cspan%20style=%22font-size:%2010pt;%22%3E%3Cspan%20style=%22font-size:%2012pt;%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGuidance-411%3C/strong%3E%3C/span%3E%3C/span%3E%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E%3Cspan%20style=%22font-size:%2010pt;%22%3EThe%20United%20Nations%20(UN)%20Declaration%20on%20the%20Rights%20of%20Indigenous%20Peoples%20and%20the%20International%20Labour%20Organization%20Convention%20169%20&lsquo;Indigenous%20and%20Tribal%20Peoples&rsquo;%20address%20the%20rights%20of%20indigenous%20peoples.&nbsp;Indigenous%20peoples%20have%20both%20collective%20and%20individual%20rights,%20as%20set%20out%20in%20these%20instruments.%20%3C/span%3E%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E%3Cspan%20style=%22font-size:%2010pt;%22%3EThe%20collective%20rights%20of%20indigenous%20peoples%20include,%20for%20example,%20the%20right%20to%20retain%20their%20own%20customs%20and%20institutions,%20and%20the%20right%20to%20self-determination.%20According%20to%20the%20UN%20Declaration%20on%20the%20Rights%20of%20Indigenous%20Peoples,%20the%20right%20to%20self-determination%20enables%20indigenous%20peoples%20to%20&lsquo;freely%20determine&nbsp;their%20political%20status%20and%20freely%20pursue%20their%20economic,%20social%20and%20cultural%20development&rsquo;%20and%20have%20the%20right&nbsp;to%20&lsquo;autonomy%20or%20self-government%20in%20matters%20relating%20to%20their%20internal%20and%20local%20affairs,%20as%20well%20as%20ways%20and%20means%20for%20financing%20their%20autonomous%20functions.&rsquo;%20Indigenous%20peoples%20also%20have%20the%20right%20to%20occupy%20and%20use%20their%20lands%20or%20territories,%20including%20those%20who%20hold%20or%20use%20land%20pursuant%20to%20informal%20or%20customary%20rights.%20Indigenous%20peoples%20cannot%20be%20relocated%20without%20free,%20prior,%20and%20informed%20consent.%20%3C/span%3E%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E%3Cspan%20style=%22font-size:%2010pt;%22%3EThey%20also%20have%20the%20right%20to%20redress%20in%20cases%20where%20their%20lands%20or%20resources%20have%20been%20occupied%20or%20damaged%20without%20their%20free,%20prior,%20and%20informed%20consent.%20Due%20diligence%20is%20expected%20of%20an%20organization%20in%20order%20to%20avoid%20infringing%20on%20the%20rights%20of%20indigenous%20peoples%20through%20its%20activities.%20An%20organization&nbsp;is%20also%20expected%20to%20respect%20the%20rights%20of%20indigenous%20peoples%20to%20free,%20prior,%20and%20informed%20consent%20in%20certain%20matters%20affecting%20them.%20This%20is%20the%20case%20when,%20for%20example,%20an%20organization%20intends%20to%20start%20operations%20on%20land%20that%20is%20inhabited%20or%20owned%20by%20indigenous%20peoples.%3C/span%3E%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E&nbsp;%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E%3Cspan%20style=%22font-size:%2012pt;%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGuidance%20for%20Disclosure%20411-1%3C/strong%3E%3C/span%3E%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3EIn%20the%20context%20of%20this%20disclosure,%20an%20&lsquo;incident&rsquo;%20refers%20to%20a%20legal%20action%20or%20complaint%20registered%20with%20the%20reporting%20organization%20or%20competent%20authorities%20through%20a%20formal%20process,%20or%20an%20instance%20of%20non-compliance%20identified%20by%20the%20organization%20through%20established%20procedures.%20Established%20procedures%20to%20identify%20instances%20of%20non-compliance%20can%20include%20management%20system%20audits,%20formal%20monitoring%20programs,%20or%20grievance%20mechanisms.%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E&nbsp;%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E%3Cstrong%3EBackground%20%3C/strong%3E%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3EThe%20number%20of%20recorded%20incidents%20involving%20the%20rights%20of%20indigenous%20peoples%20provides%20information&nbsp;about%20the%20implementation%20of%20an%20organization&rsquo;s%20policies%20relating%20to%20indigenous%20peoples.%20This%20information%20helps%20to%20indicate%20the%20state%20of%20relations%20with%20stakeholder%20communities.%20This%20is%20particularly%20important%20in%20regions%20where%20indigenous%20peoples%20reside,%20or%20have%20interests%20near%20operations%20of%20the%20organization.%3C/div%3E",
